    Note: Octal 0755 = decimal 493 = 0x1ED = S_IRWXU | S_IRGRP | S_IXGRP | S_IROTH | S_IXOTH.
    Note: Source: POSIX <sys/stat.h>; identical across MIPS Linux and asm-generic.
    Return 493
End Process

